{
  "stem": "23645.5",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "After the liberation, it was my own thoughts, or my first thought was, I wanted to go home, you know?",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's enough.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we were all euphoric.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were walking on air that we survived.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then, you know, the news started trickling in about the people that died, and how many died, and so on.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it was unbelievable.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We didn't believe the enormity of the deed.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Millions and millions had died.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You lived in your-- in your own small world, and you just went day by day, and you didn't see the big picture.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You had blinkers on your eyes, and you only saw what's in front of you.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And so as time went by, you realized the enormity of it all.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We were in Buchenwald for another three months, because all of us wanted to leave.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then there were the Americans and some people that they designated to-- to look after us were saying, look, you can't leave in here because it's a different world.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "There's no home there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Give us a chance to find-- to find who is alive and who isn't.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It was complete chaos, what was going on.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And some of the eldest among us came and started looking after us.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Suddenly-- suddenly there was a group of us that started getting childhood diseases.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Like mumps broke out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "In the camp years, we-- we didn't have time to be sick.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And suddenly we had doctors looking after us, taking our blood pressure, giving us special foods, giving us-- and taking everybody's history, and so on.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we were wandering around in-- in-- in the neighborhood.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And for the longest time, we wouldn't venture out, because you know, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] when you're enclosed, your mentality is such that you don't believe it.",
      "word_count": 28
    }
  ],
